/*
* The hostCloudAnchor() method schedules a background task that will begin the hosting process,
 but the method call returns immediately, so the app's UI thread is not blocked.
 You can check to see if the anchor was successfully hosted or not
 by polling the state of the anchor after every session.update() call.
*/

Anchor anc = session.hostCloudAnchor(hit.createAnchor());